Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting old words\Nthat have been used up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to convey\Nmy simple thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day's faint wind blows away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the castle ruins of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh with you\Nand live for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still that incident\Nwill continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it must be good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving nothing behind,\Nlet us share what is left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, we'll realize\Nthat it was everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sadness will touch our cheeks,\Ncreating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex\Nand melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That form…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s the extent of\Nthe rumored “Absolute Defense”?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see… You were wearing sand, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent’s not just him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That attack just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would’ve been dangerous\Nhad I not been protected by sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body is still…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just be a hindrance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying sand…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re first, Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He yanked out his spinal column?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vengeful Strike:\N                              The Bracken Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance of the Clematis Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bone of the strongest calcification…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will pierce you,\Nsand defense and all…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Defense: Shukaku’s Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer will\NKimimaro hold out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he should still\Nbe okay for a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did all I could with the treatment…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s not nearly enough\Ninformation about his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it’d be quite different\N if we had something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the medical history\Nand treatment data of his clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What came out after looking into it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the bloody history of how\Nthe Kaguya Clan became just him…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools who provoked the great land of\Nthe Village Hidden in the Mist into battle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with just their clan\Nand were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaguya Clan was\Na foolish clan that liked battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield was the only place\Nwhere they could be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was long ago when\Na simple-minded group
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that only enjoyed slaughter\Nwas acceptable…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The times are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing something like fighting\Nonly with power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,against a governed organization\Nlike the Mist…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can only be called an act of fools\Nrushing towards death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you saved only he\Nwho was the youngest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the most exceptional\Namong the Kaguya Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid possessed the power that\Nwould be feared even by the fighting clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems he was kept\Nin prison the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would’ve been a waste to let him…die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wouldn’t want\Nthat rare Kekkei Genkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He possesses a strong\Nand firm bone structure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a defensive power to\Nrepel all kinds of physical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if turned to offense…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bones become\Na most powerful weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because I’ve fought him once\Nthat I understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sand shield is\Nan absolute defense, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that unusual form…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be okay.\NThere’s no way it’ll be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered minerals with\Ngreat hardness from the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,applied pressure with Chakra\Nand mixed them into the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You… that unusual Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the Kekkei Genkai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaguya Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability which now\Nonly I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one of the clan, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it’ll die out here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, that might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to sickness,\Nmy body will not last so long…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the clan will not die out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides I’m not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the “Earth” Curse Mark…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become a part of you,\NLord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s get everything, Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let’s see the truth of\Nthis world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re my “Vessel of Dreams.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are presents from me.\NI hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather…die or obey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the best a team\Nof four can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll ask just once more…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you rather choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, we’re the Sound Ninja Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not alone, you said…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an existence shouldering\None part of Lord Orochimaru’s ambition…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remain inside\NLord Orochimaru’s soul…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru’s brainwashing, huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a pitiful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my big moves too much.\NI don’t have much Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amount of Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are something…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll sink and confine you\N200 meters into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the pressure of the sand\Nstuck to your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll soon be unable to move,\Nnot even a finger…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it…!\NThis time for sure you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bracken Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is annoying…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when waiting eagerly for\Nsomething you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like\Nyou’re humoring a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should know\Nthis the most, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can beat Kimimaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what hindrance\Nshould appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to do something like this;\Nvery impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was ride the sand\NI’m always controlling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to know how you use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, Lord Orochimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last… The destruction of\N the Leaf will begin…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Hokage…\NI’ll teach you a thing or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Kimimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Kazekage of\Nthe Hidden Sand Village
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is no match against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimimaro, it’s thanks to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimimaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimimaro, so you can’t go on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can’t be of use…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there’s no significance\Nto my living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is your condition, Kimimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The “Destruction of the Leaf”\Nresulted in an unfortunate near-miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Sound Ninja Four\Nhave gone to pick up a new vessel…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochimaru’s new\N “Vessel of Dreams.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru’s brainwashing, huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a pitiful guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re wrong… Far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no significance to living…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…you might be able to discover\Nsomething interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by continuing to live…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you discovered that flower…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how I discovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the “Earth” Curse Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this… I can become\Na part of you, Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s get everything, Kimimaro…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let’s see the truth of\Nthis world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to discover\Nthe truth of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Lord Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a persistent guy,\Nbut this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won’t ever come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t go on…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re getting off…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not brainwashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person…\NLord Orochimaru understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? Has Kimimaro…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The likes of Kimimaro makes\Nno difference now…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke… I can hardly wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll come here even by himself…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been totally hammered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sensei said it often…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck is also a part of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That backseat driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s not a backseat driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn’t good enough at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m grateful for you saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please don’t talk like that\Nabout my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you feel that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the honor of someone you revere\Nhas been hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you yourself are hurt badly\Nand become enraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more important the person\Nyou revere is to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greater the feeling…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clan won’t die out…\NI’m not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remain inside\NLord Orochimaru’s soul for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person,\NLord Orochimaru, understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting for the sake of someone\Nimportant to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also the same\Nas Naruto Uzumaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…the person who is important\Nto oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might not always be “virtuous.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way someone evil\Ncan be thought of as an important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Even if you know they’re “evil”…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can’t defeat solitude…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don’t feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean\N“for achieving your goal”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru wants you\Nonly as a “vessel”!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way\N I can let you go to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on going,\NI have to take you back by force!
